{"id":"2839085776","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2839085776","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjgzOTA4NTc3Ng==","status":"current","title":"Ejercicio Práctico: Añadir Promociones a Links de Pago","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"61e040e0f3037f00698228dd","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"José Bauzán","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/61e040e0f3037f00698228dd","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"José Bauzán","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_US","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=61e040e0f3037f00698228dd"}},"when":"2024-01-09T20:23:49.619Z","friendlyWhen":"Jan 09, 2024","message":"","number":7,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"3026","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$2839085776.73","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/2839085776"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2839085776/version/7"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2261417989","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2261417989","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI2MTQxNzk4OQ==","status":"current","title":"Onboarding - General","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":827},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2261417989/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2261417989/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2261417989/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2261417989/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2261417989","tinyui":"/x/BYDKhg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2261417989","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2261417989/Onboarding+-+General","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2261417989"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Se debe crear un sistema de manejo de promociones para Links de Pago en Tpago.</p><p>Cada promoci&oacute;n cuenta con un identificador &uacute;nico, un nombre y una descripci&oacute;n. Se requiere desarrollar un modelo para almacenar dichas promociones y asociarlas a los links de pago</p><p /><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Modelo de datos<br />Dise&ntilde;ar un modelo que contenga los siguientes datos para las promociones</p><ul><li><p>Identificador de la promoci&oacute;n (id)</p></li><li><p>Nombre (name)</p></li><li><p>Descripci&oacute;n (description)</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Asociar un link a una promoci&oacute;n</p><ul><li><p>Cada promoci&oacute;n debe ser creada para un link en espec&iacute;fico.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Operaciones CRUD</p><ul><li><p>Se deben tener en cuenta los siguientes casos:</p><ul><li><p>Se debe poder crear nuevas promociones y asociarlas a un link dado</p></li><li><p>Se debe poder obtener una promoci&oacute;n dado un identificador de link</p></li><li><p>Se debe poder actualizar el nombre y la descripci&oacute;n de una promoci&oacute;n dada</p></li><li><p>Se debe poder eliminar una promoci&oacute;n dada</p></li><li><p>(Opcional) Se deben poder obtener todas las promociones que se encuentren disponibles, utilizando <a href=\"https://github.com/thisisqubika/bancard-picasso-listing\">picasso-listing</a></p></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n de vistas</p><ul><li><p>(Opcional) Se debe poder visualizar las promociones creadas desde el portal de Tpago de comercios (payment-link-portal), en una nueva secci&oacute;n del men&uacute;, dando la opci&oacute;n de crear, actualizar y eliminar cada una de ellas</p></li><li><p>Al momento de que un usuario ingresa a un link para el cual haya una promoci&oacute;n asociada, se debe mostrar un mensaje con el t&iacute;tulo y la descripci&oacute;n de la promoci&oacute;n (no se necesita que se aplique ningun descuento real, simplemente mostrar el mensaje)</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Pruebas</p><ul><li><p>Se deben realizar tests utilizando Rspec</p></li></ul></li></ol><p /><p>Proyectos involucrados:</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-payment-link-portal\">bancard-payment-link-portal</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-tpago-portal\">bancard-tpago-portal</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-payment-link-service\">bancard-payment-link-service</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-left: 30.0px;\" /><p>Este ejercicio busca desarrollar un conocimiento inicial sobre el desarrollo en nuestros proyectos.</p><p /><p>Bienvenidos y mucha suerte!!</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2839085776"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":815},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2839085776/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2839085776/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2839085776/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2839085776/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2839085776","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2839085776/Ejercicio+Pr+ctico+A+adir+Promociones+a+Links+de+Pago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2839085776","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2839085776","tinyui":"/x/0AI5qQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}